sub_title: Swedish graduate student enrolled in MSc Urban Environmental Management at Wageningen University and Research, specializing in Environmental Economics
summary:
Currently enrolled in the MSc program Urban Environmental Management, majoring in Environmental Economics at Wageningen University and Research. I am proficient in R and self-taught in Python, with a deep curiosity for sustainable development and climate change.

My aim is to work at a company where I can develop new skills and build upon my existing knowledge.
